org/wiki/Book_of_Common_Prayer","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Book of Common Prayer","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705202,"age":45,"year":"1558","julianDay":2290108,"title":"Act of Uniformity","description":"The Act of Uniformity was passed by the Parliament of England and required all people to go to church once a week. The consequence of not attending church was a fine of 12 pence, which was a considerable amount for a poor person.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"When Alexander Wollacombe esq was born in 1513, in Roborough, Devon, England, his father, Thomas Wollacombe, was 64 and his mother, Thomasina Coles, was 38. He married Anne Pollard about 1529, in Devon, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 1 daughter. He died before 6 March 1568, and was buried in Roborough, Devon, England."},"et":{"1513–before 6 March 1568":"1513–enne 6. märtsi 1568","1513–1568":"1513–1568","1516–Female":"1516–Surnud","1530–1590":"1530–1590","1542–Female":"1542–Surnud","1450–Male":"1450–Surnud","1475–Female":"1475–Surnud","Abt 1529":"umbes 1529","1450":"1450","1590":"1590","before 6 March 1568":"enne 6. märtsi 1568","1558":"1558","1513":"1513","1568":"1568","1542":"1542","1475":"1475","1530":"1530","about 1530":"umbes 1530","6 March 1567/8":"6. märts 1568","1549":"1549","1516":"1516","of Way, Devonshire, England":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Roborough, Devon, England":"Roborough, Devon, England","Atherington, Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Atherington, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1513–before 6 March 1568":"1513–ennen vuotta 6. maaliskuuta 1568","1513–1568":"1513–1568","1516–Female":"1516–Kuollut","1530–1590":"1530–1590","1542–Female":"1542–Kuollut","1450–Male":"1450–Kuollut","1475–Female":"1475–Kuollut","Abt 1529":"noin 1529","1450":"1450","1590":"1590","before 6 March 1568":"ennen vuotta 6. maaliskuuta 1568","1558":"1558","1513":"1513","1568":"1568","1542":"1542","1475":"1475","1530":"1530","about 1530":"noin 1530","6 March 1567/8